{"title":"送货下乡","authors":["赵文灿"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":12,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"送货下乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖北枣阳鹿头  赵文灿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部作风大转变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处难找一人闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙罢工作搞生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送货下乡到田间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咯支支，咯支支，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推的推来担的担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产资料消费品，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样货物带的全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张大嫂买条新手巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李大叔买盒好纸烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去赶集二十里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在送货真方便，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑子放在地头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解起镰刀下了田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又销货来又劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少都称赞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}